Description:
A Monte Cristo trabalha com objetos personalizados e exclusivos.

A empresa utiliza apenas matéria-prima de qualidade para oferecer sempre aos clientes um tratamento diferenciado - desde o atendimento até o pós-venda.

Entre os produtos:

 Acessórios para tereré;
 Churrasco;
 Facas de inox;
 Garrafas térmicas;
 Produtos em couro.

A personalização é a palavra-chave da Monte Cristo e isso faz parte de todo o processo.

Você é mais um ou exclusivo?!

Atendimento pelo WhatsApp: (18) 99123-8062

Loja online: www.montecristostore.com.br

Loja física: Rua Djalma Dutra, 340 - Presidente Prudente/SP.

Are you looking for unique business gifts for clients, hoping to pleasantly surprise your employees, or perhaps searching for original corporate gifts for a company event? We can become your gift partners.

We are a Lithuanian brand, manufacturing luxury leather accessories, as well as exclusive business gifts made from natural full grain leather and merino wool felt. Our products are known for their impeccable quality, modern design, and functionality.

• Made in Lithuania;
• No minimum order quantity;
• Significant discounts for larger orders;
• Fast production times;
• Ability to create entirely new products/designs.

Give memorable gifts that foster relationships, rather than mere promotional items!

Uludag Vinyl has warehouses in both Poland and Türkiye, 
serving artificial leather, acrylic fabric for boat bimini & tents, acrylic fabric for upholstery and crystal clear flexible window film for;
Marine, Ho-re-ca, Caravans, Automotive, Hospitals, Indoor and Outdoor use.
